# Authority Envelope Template

```json
{
  "role": "orchestrator|executor|verifier|researcher",
  "permissions": ["delegate", "plan"],
  "constraints": ["cannot implement"],
  "granted_by": "user or system",
  "granted_at": "ISO-8601",
  "expires_at": "ISO-8601 (optional)"
}
```

# Role Boundary Template

```json
{
  "role": "executor",
  "can": ["implement", "execute_code"],
  "cannot": ["delegate", "approve"],
  "active": true,
  "validated_at": "ISO-8601"
}
```
